title: AIIMS Deoghar Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for 174 Senior Resident Posts
description: The All India Institute of Medical Sciences Deoghar (AIIMS Deoghar) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 174 Senior Resident Posts. The interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their BDS, MDS, MD/MS, post-graduation, and DNB can apply for the AIIMS Deogarh Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can apply in offline mode.
